{"tid":555053,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"美國 AirPods 冒煙爆炸險燒傷耳朵！Apple 表示密切跟進","createTime":"2018-02-09T05:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T03:51:16.000Z","uid":39628,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"5200b70dc23d7346adaff9505067820311fb6dac","tid":555053,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:44:27.000Z","msg":"Apple iPhone 的爆炸事故就時有聽聞，但 AirPods 耳機爆炸，大家又有否聽過呢？據外媒報道，最近一位來自美國佛羅里達的市民 Jason Colon，提到自己在當地一間健身室做 gym 期間，戴在右耳的 AirPods 耳機離奇冒煙爆炸（見大圖），兼有火花產生！幸好 Jason Colon 及時發現 AirPods 有問題而將之摘掉，才不至於燒傷耳朵，總算是不幸中之大幸。<br />\n<br />\nJason Colon 表示慶幸自己及時發現 AirPods 冒煙，才不至令右耳受傷，不過說不定右耳垂部分或有受傷，因為事發期間，AirPods 耳機是戴在耳上。當然，事件一出，Apple 強調會密切跟進事件，並跟 Jason Colon 聯絡了解事發經過，了解並調查  AirPods 出現問題的主因。<br />\n<br />\n雖然以上例子只屬個別事件，不過都提提大家，如發現電子產品外觀、操作出現異常，還是即時停用以保安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2005000/2009258/20180209_AirPods_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2005000%2F2009258%2F20180209_AirPods_01_1024.jpg&h=6d29e8f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2009258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2009258&d=g2lStspYMc9BVbsoXhqxwywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c9ad8a46\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2009258</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無線耳機係咪第一次爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7776e32a705dcdcf582d1d1efa011274bac7730","tid":555053,"uid":52215,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:45:28.000Z","msg":"下次用airpod當手榴彈"},{"pid":"624236363eaf7a0f6af8d2febfc31e06a8b44977","tid":555053,"uid":73356,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T05:50:29.000Z","msg":"電池又爆 耳機又爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee40ff8d5e28b66b8475443d